data.description: Come check out this beautiful 4 bed 3 full bath home that is very conveniently located to Enterprise, Fort Novosel, and Dothan. As you enter you will notice the natural light that highlights all of the wonderful features of the home. There is a formal dining room with access to the updated kitchen. The kitchen boasts ample counter space and a spacious pantry. The eat in dining area is perfect for enjoying breakfast as you look out into the backyard. The primary bedroom has a separate shower and jetted tub, as well as a spacious closet. The flooring and carpeting in the home have been recently updated. The oversized backyard is perfect for fall evenings to enjoy the cool nights! The shed in the backyard will convey with the home. Don't miss your opportunity to make this home your own. VA assumable loan at 5.125% available to buyers that qualify.
